                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, N</hi> 259). I produce a certificate of Hearn's conviction, from Clerkenwell—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted Nov. 1847, and confined four months</hi>)—I was present; he is the person.</p>
